The problem with being in your 40's in a 50+ guild can be dealt with several ways:<P>Finding another guild (it sounds like you don't want to do this)<P>Getting guild members to help powerlevel you (some don't care for this, but it is worth trying)<P>Trying to recruit more 40's to your guild (your guild might not go along)<P>If these are not viable options, reconsider your feelings on the first one. Having a good guild is somewhat critical at upper levels for anyone who has any trouble getting a group (nonclerics and nonenchanters). If all your guild is giving you is some chatter to listen in on, well...
